nz.co.jedsimson.lgp.core.environment.constants

Class DoubleConstantLoader

  • GenericConstantLoader
    • nz.co.jedsimson.lgp.core.environment.constants.DoubleConstantLoader
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ComponentLoader<TComponent>, ConstantLoader<T>, Module

    public class DoubleConstantLoader
extends GenericConstantLoader

    An implementation of interface ConstantLoader that loads constants as a collection of Doubles.

    We get around having to implement a lot of this ourselves by subclassing class GenericConstantLoader with a parsing function suitable for converting the raw strings to doubles.

    See Also:
    interface ConstantLoader, Double, class GenericConstantLoader, class GenericConstantLoader
